To deploy to TOM CAT use the below steps (this can and will be automated later)

1)  Download and install tomcat -> make sure it can run
2)  In the tomcat webapps directory create a new folder, call it project
3)  Inside this project file create a WEB-INF directory
4)  Inside the WEB-INF directory create the following directories
        i)  classes
        ii) lib
5) Copy the contents of the resources/jar folder into lib
6) Copy the contents of the out/ folder into classes
7) Copy web.xml from the root directory into the root of WEB-INF
8) Start / Restart TOM CAT
9) Run testsuite